00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:05.950
Evet, elimizden geleni yapalım, Renji, Ichigo!  

00:03:06.150 --> 00:03:08.580
Ha? Ben de mi dahilim?  

00:03:21.100 --> 00:03:23.940
Bu coşku da ne?  

00:03:23.940 --> 00:03:26.120
